<!DOCTYPE suite SYSTEM "https://testng.org/testng-1.0.dtd">

<suite name="Smoke Test Suite" verbose="1">
    <listeners>
        <listener class-name="myapp.utilities.ListenersUtils"></listener>
    </listeners>
    <test name="Smoke Test">
        <packages>
            <package name="myapp.tests.smoketest"/>
        </packages>
    </test>
</suite>
<!--
    1. xml files are used to RUN existing test cases
    2. Suite > test > packages > groups > classes > methods
    3. Verbose is OPTIONAL ... it is only the amount of info that you see on the console, bigger number; more info you get
    4. SAVE THE XML FILE FIRST, then run it
    5. If the path is not correct, we see 'NO Test were found' error
    -->